Package: ggragged
Title: Ragged Grids for ggplot2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Mikko", "Marttila", , "mikkmart@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Faceting functions for defining panel layouts arranged in a
    grid with ragged edges in ggplot2. These can be useful, for example,
    to represent nested or partially crossed relationships between
    faceting variables.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    ggplot2
Imports:
    gtable,
    rlang,
    vctrs
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Collate: 
    'facet_ragged.R'
    'facet_ragged_rows.R'
    'facet_ragged_cols.R'
    'ggragged-package.R'
